The `%prep` phase fails because the source tarball extracts to `oterm-0.13.0` (hyphen), but the RPM script attempts to `cd oterm_0.13.0` (underscore). Update your `%autosetup` or `%setup` macro call in the spec file to explicitly specify the correct directory with `-n oterm-0.13.0`. No additional dependencies are missing for this specific error; correcting the extraction path will allow the build to proceed to the `%build` phase where `%pyproject_wheel` handles backend resolution automatically.